I love chorales - voice, strings, bugles, I don’t care. I love hearing them and I love writing them. Here’s a bit I arranged and played for an upcoming @bandamagda project. @magdagiannikou is one of my favorite musicians on the planet in so many ways and I can’t wait for y’all to hear what she’s cooking up @yamahamusicusa #trumpet #chorale #logicprox #newmusic

On March 10th, 2023 the moon will be in a Waning Gibbous phase, it will have an illumination of 92% and @bandamagda will release new music. 🌖

Illustrated by @amandamijangos & @fuenteseca

“One more day till the release!” sang the bluebird. 🔹

Illustrated by @fuenteseca & @amandamijangos

With this new song, Leleyo (Kissing in the Dark) we wish you a spring full of love, forests & fantasy. It’s out, take a listen, we hope it fills your hearts as it did ours. 

Performed and arranged by @magdagiannikou @malenamarcase @justinmstanton @boblanzetti @jordanperlson @aronoffmatt 

Written by @malenamarcase @justinmstanton @magdagiannikou 

Recorded at @fluxstudiosnyc by @tomfoolery11235 & @j_welshman 

Produced by @magdagiannikou 

Vocal production by @malenamarcase 

Mixed by @tomfoolery11235 

Illustrations by @fuenteseca @amandamijangos 

Special thanks to @lucabbordonaro & @funky_chico

Not sure how @jordanperlson does it, making things dark and bright at the same time, subtle and powerful, unique but also familiar. 

While the track moves along with practically no use of cymbals, it still has so much dynamic contour and storytelling. And fun 🐇 🔹✨🌿

#teamleleyo

“.. La luna espera sonriente con su mágico esplendor, la llegada del valiente y alegre pescador…” 🌞

A precious @bandamagda set for you, Valencia, tomorrow night at @offsala . This initiative of colleague & friend @mineerkaya has inspired dozens of volunteers that have put love, time and effort in putting together this show in support of children affected by the recent earthquake in Turkey & Syria. Let’s sell it out, shall we?
